Note: To protect against unauthorized file retrieval an administrator must
set the _filesPathWhiteListRegExp property in "SiteScope root directory"
\groups\master.config file to a regular expression of the paths that may be
monitored. If the file path is not compliant with the regular expression set,
an error is encountered when configuring the monitor for Log File and File
monitors or at runtime for Multi Log monitor.

